Work Experience:

 Worked as Sales Executive for CHERMAS SHOWROOM Ameerpet, Hyderabad for 2

years.

 Worked as a Sales Executive and Casual Department Incharge for LIFE STYLE

INTERNATIONAL PVT LTD Begumpet, Hyderabad for 6 years.

My Role at work:

My role in this organization is to sale the Garments, Stock Checking, Stock replacement,

Customer Service, Giving good service to Customers.

Preparing Chart file of Stock replacement, Stock on the Floor, Sale for the Day, Sale for

the Month.

Preparing Chart file for the garments by Model, by Pants or Shirts, by Size, by Color, by

Barcode.

Preparing Chart file for the Go-down Stock as Chart file is done for Show room Stock.

 Worked as a Backend Office staff for ORANGE HONDA Tolichowki Hyderabad for 2

years.

 Worked as a Assistant Administrator for THE FUTURE KIDS SCHOOL

Nanakramguda Gachibowli for 4 years.

My Role at work:

I work very sincerely.

I type the Question papers which are hand written by the teachers.

I set the question papers, Work Sheets which are given to students.

I take Photos and Videos of Functions, Festival celebrations, Sports, Activities and

presentations given by students which useful to keep them in Website.

I do give SMS to the parents regarding Daily Programme Schedule details, Home Work

and Class Work, Parties Notes which happen in the School.

I will send the message one day before, if it is important and it is about meeting I will

send it 2days or 3days before, to inform the parents that something going to happen in

the School. Please make sure that you dont miss the meeting.

I will take admissions and undertake Uniforms and Books.
